o/playerIndex?id=2929512">"Wikipedia Editor Revealed as Fake"</a> <span style="font-size:85%;">(video)</span>. <i><a href="/wiki/ABC_News" title="ABC News">ABC News</a></i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">March 8,</span> 2007</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEssjay+controversy&amp;rft.atitle=Wikipedia+Editor+Revealed+as+Fake&amp;rft.aufirst=Dan&amp;rft.aulast=Harris&amp;rft.date=2007-03-06&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=ABC+News&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FVideo%2FplayerIndex%3Fid%3D2929512&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-Cohen-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Cohen_10-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Cohen_10-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Cohen_10-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web">Noam Cohen (March 6, 2007). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20070308074804/http://www.iht.com/articles/2007/03/06/business/wiki.php">"Wikipedia ire turns against ex-editor"</a>. <i>International Herald Tribune</i>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.iht.com/articles/2007/03/06/business/wiki.php">the original</a> on March 8, 2007<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">September 30,</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEssjay+controversy&amp;rft.atitle=Wikipedia+ire+turns+against+ex-editor&amp;rft.au=Noam+Cohen&amp;rft.date=2007-03-06&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=International+Herald+Tribune&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iht.com%2Farticles%2F2007%2F03%2F06%2Fbusiness%2Fwiki.php&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="displa